---
title: Slow-Cooked Satay Beef & Bacon Garlic Rice with Veggies & Crushed Peanuts
description: Imagine this: tender, melt-in-your-mouth beef infused with a rich, creamy peanut sauce, slow-cooked to perfection. Now, stop
imagining, start cooking! Throw everything in your slow cooker and forget about it for a meal that proves that slow and steady
wins the dinner race!

*We’ve replaced the crushed peanuts in this recipe with roasted
almonds due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
